OL,3,C'We're not declaring bankruptcy':
OL,4,CStormont warned over spending spree
OL,6,FThe Westminster Treasury has told UTV
OL,7,Fany Stormont overspend would represent
OL,8,F"serious financial mismanagement".
OL,10,FNorthern Ireland ministers are already
OL,11,Ffacing a projected overspend of almost
OL,12,F#700million.
OL,14,FHowever, despite those pressures, the
OL,15,FDepartment of Health was allowed to
OL,16,Ftake #100m from next year's budget to
OL,17,Ffund a pay rises for workers.
OL,19,FFinance Minister John O'Dowd, however,
OL,20,Fsaid the Executive would continue to
OL,21,Fprovide front line services.
