OL,3,C'We're not declaring bankruptcy':
OL,4,CStormont warned over spending spree
OL,6,F"We aren't declaring bankruptcy," he
OL,7,Ftold UTV.
OL,9,FIn a statement a UK Government
OL,10,Fspokesman said: "The Executive are
OL,11,Fresponsible for balancing their budget
OL,12,Fwithin their record high funding
OL,13,Fsettlement from the UK Government,
OL,14,Fwhich is over #18billion in 2025-26.
OL,16,F"This is above Northern Ireland's
OL,17,Findependently assessed level of need,
OL,18,Fwhich was agreed by the Executive.
