OL,3,C'We're not declaring bankruptcy':
OL,4,CStormont warned over spending spree
OL,6,FDepartments were overcommitted to the
OL,7,Ftotal of #665m, excluding #120m for
OL,8,FPSNI data breach. That brings the
OL,9,Ftotal to #785 million for this year
OL,10,Falone.
